Twelve Stars is only meant to be a slight reference here, but it's going to be expanded more in the series SCP-3417 is a part of. The two dots are just how much of the universe is left (only two stars). Rakmou-leusan was killed by the Voruteut (the invasion was far too much to handle). The sun's motives are either A) It wants to protect the people in the solar system, or B) It only wants to protect itself from the invasion. The spiral was meant to suggest that SCP-2821 killed SCP-3417.

Feel free to ask any other questions if you have them!







